headline: Amazon Is Planning Walmart-Style Big Box Store Near Chicago
summary: If approved by officials in the Chicago suburb of Orland Park, Amazon could begin construction later this year.  Earlier this month, the village planning commission reviewed the project, which has been endorsed by Mayor Jim Dodge.

headline: Is Target's (TGT) Big Wellness Push Reframing Its Core Brand Narrative for Investors?
summary: In early January 2026, Target announced a 30% expansion of its wellness assortment, adding thousands of new, often exclusive products across food, beverage, baby, beauty, health, and apparel, while brands like RYZE mushroom coffee, Tubby Todd, Naked Life, Nara Organics, and First Day revealed their first national Target launches. This coordinated push positions Target as a broader wellness destination, linking everything from functional drinks to infant formula and family skincare under one...
